To check out a particular version: get -rsid file
To check out version before a particular time: get -cdate-time file
          date-time: yy[mm[dd[hh[mm[ss]]]]]

To remove a leaf delta:  	sccs rmdel -rsid file
To change a delta comment:	sccs cdc -rsid -y"comment" file
To generate script to combine SCCS deltas:	sccs comb -csid1-sid2 file
